{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "i-Tours-API",
    "name": "i-Tours API",
    "description": "API collection for i-Tours - Intelligent Destination Selection System\n\n## 🔐 Registration Flow (OTP Verification)\n\n### Step 1: Sign Up\n- Call `POST /users/signup` with your details\n- You'll receive an OTP code in your email\n- Response: `{ message: 'Verification code sent...', email: '...' }`\n\n### Step 2: Verify OTP\n- Call `POST /users/verify-otp` with your email and the OTP code from your inbox\n- On success: User is created, JWT token is returned and auto-saved\n- Response: `{ user: {...}, accessToken: '...', message: 'Welcome to i-Tours!' }`\n\n### Resend OTP (Optional)\n- If OTP expired or not received, call `POST /users/resend-otp`\n\n## 🔑 Already have an account?\n- Call `POST /users/signin` with email and password\n- JWT token is auto-saved to `accessToken` variable\n\n## 📌 Using Protected Endpoints\nAll other endpoints require the `Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}` header (already configured).",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "description": "Authentication endpoints - Sign up with OTP verification and Sign in",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Step 1 - Sign Up (Send OTP)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"firstName\": \"John\",\n  \"lastName\": \"Doe\",\n  \"email\": \"test@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\",\n  \"preferences\": {}\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/signup",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "users",
                "signup"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Step 1: Initiate registration. Sends OTP verification code to the provided email address."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Step 2 - Verify OTP (Complete Registration)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (jsonData.accessToken) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', jsonData.accessToken);",
                  "    console.log('Token saved successfully!');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"test@example.com\",\n  \"otp\": \"123456\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/verify-otp",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "users",
                "verify-otp"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Step 2: Verify OTP code sent to email. On success, creates user account and returns JWT token."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Resend OTP",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"test@example.com\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/resend-otp",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "users",
                "resend-otp"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Resend OTP code if the previous one expired or was not received."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Sign In",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (jsonData.accessToken) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', jsonData.accessToken);",
                  "    console.log('Token saved successfully!');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"test@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/signin",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "users",
                "signin"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Login with existing account. Returns JWT token."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
